Kitten, the [Kit](https://www.kitlang.org) package manager.

---

Want a fancy badge to tell users they can install your code with Kitten? Copy the following url in the markdown code and replace `mypackage` with the name of your package. If you have a website you want to link to for your package, like documentation or a getting started guide, replace the &link= link with your link to have the right side link to your page. If not, remove it and the entire badge will link to Kitten. See [https://shields.io/](https://shields.io/) for more info.
